# News Summarization & Hindi TTS Application  

## Overview  
This application extracts news articles about a given company, performs sentiment analysis, and generates a Hindi audio summary using Text-to-Speech (TTS).  

### Features  
âœ… **News Extraction** â€“ Fetches real-time news articles related to a company.  
âœ… **Sentiment Analysis** â€“ Classifies news as Positive, Negative, or Neutral.  
âœ… **Comparative Analysis** â€“ Compares sentiment trends across articles.  
âœ… **Hindi Text-to-Speech** â€“ Converts sentiment summary into Hindi audio.  
âœ… **Interactive Web UI** â€“ Built using **Streamlit** for easy access.  

