## Installation  

### **1ï¸Clone the Repository**  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/news-summarization-tts.git
cd news-summarization-tts


#Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt


#Run the Application
streamlit run app.py


#Usage  
1ï¸ Enter a company name (e.g., "Tesla") in the search bar.
2ï¸ Click Fetch News to extract articles.
3ï¸ View sentiment analysis results for each news article.
4ï¸ Listen to the Hindi audio summary generated from the sentiment analysis.

